        "description": "<p>This plugin can represent tabular numeric data, functions or some kinds of quality structure and provides different info.<\/p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bblockswp.com\/demo\/chart\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Demos<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<h4>Features<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fully Customizable<\/strong>: All the options you need to arrange the showcase to your liking are available here.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Different Types<\/strong>: Chart block comes with different types, you can easily switch the type of chart.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>How to use<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First, install the Chart Block plugin<\/li>\n<li>Add the Chart Block from the block category called &#8220;Widgets&#8221; in the Gutenberg editor.<\/li>\n<li>You can change block settings from the right-side settings sidebar.<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Enjoy!<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>For Installation help click on Installation Tab<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Feedback<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Did you like this plugin? Dislike it? Do you have a feature request?equest? <a href=\"mailto:&#115;u&#x70;&#112;&#x6f;&#114;&#x74;&#064;&#x62;&#112;l&#x75;&#103;&#x69;&#110;&#x73;&#046;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;\" title=\"Send feedback\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Please share your feedback with us<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>\u2b50 Check out the Parent Plugin of this plugin-<\/h4>\n<p>\ud83d\udd25 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bblockswp.com\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">b Blocks<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Best gutenberg blocks collections for WordPress.<\/p>\n<h4>\u2b50 Check out our other WordPress Plugins-<\/h4>\n<p>\ud83d\udd25 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bplugins.com\/products\/html5-audio-player\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Html5 Audio Player<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Play .mp3, .wav, and .ogg audio files in WordPress.<\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udd25 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bplugins.com\/products\/html5-video-player\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Html5 Video Player<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Best video player plugin for WordPress.<\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udd25 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bplugins.com\/products\/pdf-poster\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">PDF Poster<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 A fully-featured PDF Viewer Plugin for WordPress.<\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udd25 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bplugins.com\/products\/document-embedder\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Document Embedder<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Embed Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Apple Pages, Psd, Pdf and more.<\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udd25 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bplugins.com\/products\/3d-viewer\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">3D Viewer<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Display interactive 3D models on the webs.<\/p>\n<p>\ud83d\udd25 <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bplugins.com\/products\/advanced-post-block\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Advanced Post Block<\/a><\/strong> \u2013 Display your Posts, Custom Post Content and Blogs in a professional way!<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<h4>From Gutenberg Editor:<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to the WordPress Block\/Gutenberg Editor<\/li>\n<li>Search For <strong>Chart Block<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Click on the <strong>Chart Block<\/strong> to add the block<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h4>Download &amp; Upload:<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the <strong>Chart Block<\/strong> plugin (<em>.zip file<\/em>)<\/li>\n<li>In your admin area, go to the Plugins menu and click on <strong>Add New<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Click on <strong>Upload Plugin<\/strong> and choose the <strong><code>chart-block.zip<\/code><\/strong> file and click on <strong>Install Now<\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin and Enjoy!<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h4>Manually:<\/h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Download and upload the <strong>Chart Block<\/strong> plugin to the <strong><code>\/wp-content\/plugins\/<\/code><\/strong> directory<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the Plugins menu in WordPress<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='is%20chart%20block%20free%3F'>\nIs Chart Block free?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, Chart Block is a free Gutenberg block plugin.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='does%20it%20work%20with%20any%20wordpress%20theme%3F'>\nDoes it work with any WordPress theme?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, it will work with any standard WordPress theme.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='can%20i%20change%20block%20settings%3F'>\nCan I change block settings?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, you can change block settings from the Gutenberg block editor&#8217;s right sidebar.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='how%20many%20times%20can%20i%20reuse%20a%20block%3F'>\nHow many times can I reuse a block?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can use unlimited times as you want.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='where%20can%20i%20get%20support%3F'>\nWhere can I get support?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can post your questions on the <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/support\/plugin\/chart-block\/\" rel=\"ugc\">support forum here<\/a><\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.1.6<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix Border Issue<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Performance Improvement<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add translate feature<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Reduce PHP Code<\/li>\n<li>Performance Improvement<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add option for height<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Reduce PHP Code<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add option for show hide X or Y scales<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.5<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add option for showing hide grid lines<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.4<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add the download option for the chart<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.3<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Performance upgrade<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.2<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update theme and Colors<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.1<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Add an option to change the point size<\/li>\n<li>Fix border size when hovering<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Release<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2615223\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=2615223\" alt=\"Line Chart\"><\/a><p>Line Chart<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2615223\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=2615223\" alt=\"Bar Chart with Subtitle\"><\/a><p>Bar Chart with Subtitle<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2615223\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-3.png?rev=2615223\" alt=\"Pie Chart with Text, Background and Grid line color\"><\/a><p>Pie Chart with Text, Background and Grid line color<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2615223\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-4.png?rev=2615223\" alt=\"Rader Chart without Title\"><\/a><p>Rader Chart without Title<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2615223\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-5.png?rev=2615223\" alt=\"Doughnut Chart\"><\/a><p>Doughnut Chart<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-6.png?rev=2615223\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/chart-block\/assets\/screenshot-6.png?rev=2615223\" alt=\"Polar Area Chart\"><\/a><p>Polar Area Chart<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Spot on<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/wigglypoppins\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/25595bc9611684fc7ba83f294f316a0b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/25595bc9611684fc7ba83f294f316a0b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/wigglypoppins\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">wigglypoppins<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 26, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Really great plugin and does almost everything I need it to out of the box, thanks!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">It would be good if you had more control over your dataset keys to change font size or have them appear on the respective data point permanently (like they do on hover)<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Also a possible addition to your chart types could be a demographic display with 100 people icons and highlighting a percentage of them relative to your data<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muy buen plugin<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/luisglave\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/e8e04e3701eba2866ba229b75d96a1cd?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/e8e04e3701eba2866ba229b75d96a1cd?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/luisglave\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">luisglave<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 21, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p class=\"\">Cumple con todas mis necesidades de publicar gr\u00e1ficos en mi sitio web<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good Value and well designed UI<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tzah\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/75aa7e54e32f245462c44f35f674cebe?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/75aa7e54e32f245462c44f35f674cebe?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tzah\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tzah<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 21, 2023<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I was searching for plugin with an option to change the colors and styles of the graphs. This plugin is so far is the best one I have tested.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It works well and I hope more features will be added to improve the product.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works well, but could be smarter<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/drywallbmb\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7c7212e5c1127458f0b14758d44f7ac4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7c7212e5c1127458f0b14758d44f7ac4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/drywallbmb\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ben Byrne <small>(drywallbmb)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 20, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">I'm pretty happy with how this block works, it solves a need I had. But it's annoying that it enqueues its JavaScript on every page on my site, instead of just the pages that include the block. Best practice for Blocks is to load assets on-demand rather than universally, so my site's PageSpeed score has gone down due to using this plugin.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Neat!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/udayrajesh\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/e5f0faaa6f60c923f66d471351a8c26e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/e5f0faaa6f60c923f66d471351a8c26e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/udayrajesh\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Rajesh <small>(udayrajesh)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 17, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">No other third party dependencies!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Generally speaking, he gets the job done!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/maportugal\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9bfa8ca2bb97c1fdfda63da46c64c41e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/9bfa8ca2bb97c1fdfda63da46c64c41e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/maportugal\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">maportugal<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 20, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">It's not as fully flexible in settings as I'd expected it to be, despite containing a significant collection of options.\nGenerally speaking, he gets the job done. I had problems with the Async JavaScript plugin, which I resolved to disable to make the graphics plugin work.\nLooking forward to new versions, more features, animations, etc...<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/zaphodbeeblebrox01\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5f59be43ee61db58fa8c015bb422cee3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/5f59be43ee61db58fa8c015bb422cee3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/zaphodbeeblebrox01\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">zaphodbeeblebrox01<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 1, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">I just needed to show a few charts and couldn't find a simple solution. This works just great! I was a bit worried since it has less than 10 installs, but it seems to be pretty new. \n\nI just have one suggestion to imporove usability: \nIt would be great if you could have a global color for a dataset (if it has the same color for all intervals). This way you don't need to change every single color by hand. \n\nThanks!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Freaking Awesome.<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nick6352683\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/91e8faddd8ea5b552e8f98ac0f15c575?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/91e8faddd8ea5b552e8f98ac0f15c575?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/nick6352683\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nick6352683<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">October 17, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">UPDATE: Oct. 17, 2021: The new update addresses the Point sizes, and it made my weekend !!! I want to criticize it,but there is nothing I can find... well done !\n\nThis is probably my favorite chart plugin, I just wish we could resize the Points independently from the Border Width - we need a separate control for the Point sizes... Other than that, this is perfect.\n\nThis plugin is really good for small data sets, which will serve probably 99% of all cases, but because there are no data import functions, not ideal for large datasets...\n\nOverall, a really impressive Gutenberg plugin !\n\nThanks,\nNick.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
